wdi2-TX.VAL.MRCH.R1.ZS.def: Merchandise exports to low- and middle-income economies in East Asia and Pacific are the sum of merchandise exports from the reporting economy to low- and middle-income economies in the East Asia and Pacific region according to World Bank classification of economies. Data are as a percentage of total merchandise exports by the economy.
wdi2-TX.VAL.MRCH.R1.ZS.name: Merchandise exports to low- and middle-income economies in East Asia & Pacific
wdi2-TX.VAL.MRCH.R1.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates based data from International Monetary Fund's Direction of Trade database.
